From Subject Re Riceburner Respect In article Saint Craig writes No anyone who is a true rider with the real riding attitude will offer a wave weather they are on a Harley or on a Honda or some other bike inless they have a serious case of my bike is better than your and you're too low to be I may not wave I just wink at you with one 'Course it's hard to see that through a shield and sunglasses but hey if you're a true rider with the real riding attitude you'll sense Chuck Rogers